column2: (let ((err (condition-case err (neovm-precompile-file "/tmp/neovm-precompile-missing-source.el") (error err)))) (and (eq (car err) 'file-error) (stringp (cadr err)) (not (null (string-match-p "Cannot read source file for precompile" (cadr err)))) (not (null (string-match-p "neovm-precompile-missing-source\\.el" (cadr err))))))
